personal.intro: These are some projects either developed due to a personal use case or just for the fun of it. Some of them are used and contributed to by a not inconsiderable number of people, as I've chosen to make them free and open source.

openSource.intro: These projects are started and developed either by me with other people, or I have contributed to already existing codebases, i.e. they are more of a community-effort than pure personal ambition.
